#. Tag: title
#: locate.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate &GUI; Frontend"
msgstr "ज्ञातव्यं &GUI; अग्रभागः"

#. Tag: primary
#: locate.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate"
msgstr "स्थानं ज्ञातव्यम्"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; has a &GUI; front end for the <command>locate</command> command "
"(findutils). Locate is used for fast file searching not from a folder but a "
"database. The package contains among other files, <command>locate</command> "
"and <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</command> goes through "
"the local file system and stores the file entries in the database. "
"<command>cron</command> often calls <command>updatedb</command> every night "
"(set with <application>KCron</application>). Choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locate...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to "
"start this feature. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> "
"can set additional arguments for <command>updatedb</command>."
msgstr ""
"&amp;krusader; एकं &amp;GUI अस्ति; अग्रभागस्य कृते<command> स्थानं ज्ञातव्यम्</command> "
"आज्ञा (findutils)। Locate इत्यस्य उपयोगः द्रुतसञ्चिका-अन्वेषणाय न तु पुटतः अपितु "
"दत्तांशकोशात् भवति । संकुलस्य अन्यसञ्चिकासु, .<command> स्थानं ज्ञातव्यम्</command> "
"तथा<command> अद्यतनं ख</command> .<command> अद्यतनं ख</command> "
"स्थानीयसञ्चिकातन्त्रेण गत्वा सञ्चिकाप्रविष्टयः दत्तांशकोशे संगृह्णाति ।<command> क्रोन</"
"command> प्रायः आह्वयति<command> अद्यतनं ख</command> प्रतिरात्रं (सेट् "
"सह<application> केक्रोन</application> ). चिनोतु<menuchoice><guimenu> उपकरणाः</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> स्थानं ज्ञातव्यम्...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> वा<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"> &amp;Ctrl;&amp;शिफ्ट;<keycap> ल</keycap></keycombo> एतत् "
"विशेषता आरभ्यतुं ।<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\"> विन्यासकर्ता</link> कृते "
"अतिरिक्त-तर्कं सेट् कर्तुं शक्नोति<command> अद्यतनं ख</command> ."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checkbox Options"
msgstr "चेकबॉक्स विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show only the existing files</guilabel>: if the database contains "
"entries which no longer exist any more (deleted, moved since the last "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>locate</command> does not list them. "
"It checks the existence of each file before the listing in the results "
"window (slow)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>केवलं विद्यमानसञ्चिकाः दर्शयतु</guilabel>: यदि दत्तांशकोशे एतादृशाः प्रविष्टयः "
"सन्ति ये पुनः नास्ति (विलोपनाः, अन्तिम <command>updatedb</command> इत्यस्मात् "
"स्थानान्तरिताः), तर्हि <command>locate</command> करोति न तान् सूचीबद्धं कुर्वन्तु। एतत् "
"परिणामविण्डो (मन्दम्) सूचीकरणात् पूर्वं प्रत्येकस्य सञ्चिकायाः अस्तित्वं परीक्षते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel>: unchecking it allows lower and upper "
"case search."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>अक्षरसंवेदनशीलः</guilabel>: तस्य अचेकं कृत्वा लघु-बृहत्-अक्षर-अन्वेषणं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action buttons"
msgstr "क्रिया बटन"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Locate</guibutton>: executes <command>locate <replaceable>foo "
"foo</replaceable></command> and places its output into the results window."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Locate</guibutton>: <command>locate <replaceable>foo foo</"
"replaceable></command> इति निष्पादयति तथा च तस्य निर्गमं परिणामविण्डो मध्ये स्थापयति "
"।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: stops the locating process."
msgstr "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: स्थाननिर्धारणप्रक्रिया स्थगयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: starts <command>updatedb</command> for "
"updating the locate database after entering the root password."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: मूलगुप्तशब्दं प्रविष्ट्वा locate दत्तांशकोशस्य "
"अद्यतनीकरणार्थं <command>updatedb</command> आरभते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: closes the locate window."
msgstr "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: locate विण्डो पिधायति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Results window"
msgstr "परिणामविण्डो"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on an item: steps to its folder, makes the item visible and "
"closes the locate dialog."
msgstr ""
"कस्यचित् द्रव्यस्य उपरि द्विवारं क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु: तस्य समुच्चय प्रति पदानि स्थापयति, द्रव्यं "
"दृश्यमानं करोति तथा च locate संवादं बन्दं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right click: edits/views/finds the menu."
msgstr "राइट् क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु: मेनू सम्पादयति/दृश्यति/अन्विषति।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>: views the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F3</keycap>: वर्तमानं द्रव्यं पश्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>: edits the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F4</keycap>: वर्तमानं द्रव्यं सम्पादयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: finds files "
"in the results window."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: परिणामविण्डो "
"मध्ये सञ्चिकाः अन्वेषयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"next search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: अग्रिमम् "
"अन्वेषणफलं दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"previous search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: पूर्वसन्धानफलं "
"दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results window supports dragging items to other windows and copy to "
"clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"परिणामविण्डो अन्यविण्डोषु वस्तूनि कर्षयितुं क्लिपबोर्डं प्रति प्रतिलिपिं कर्तुं च समर्थयति "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) ।"
